de.adorsys.datasafe.types.api.context.annotations

Annotation Type RuntimeDelegate


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface RuntimeDelegate
    This annotation enables the capability of runtime-delegation using OverridesRegistry as context. It generates delegating class that wraps original class and provides extension point to change functionality provided by original class functionality. If override is present in OverridesRegistry then method from registry will be called, otherwise original method is called. Code generation is done by RuntimeDelegateProcessor.
